text:
The Roast Pork stall is good. I ordered mixed plate of Roast Duck; Pork & Char Siew with 2 plates of Noodles for $18.  Lots of meat in the plate and good taste too!

Would definitely go back for more.  Also this kopitiam allows 5 to Dine-In too!

Good food but some are expensive if you can afford otherwise look for budget meal,eat once or twice depends on housework n my diabetic. Hope one day i can find brown rice here due to diabetes. Thanks üëç everything. I will buy rice cooker n toaster one day when gst vocher comes n pay my hospital emergency bills n other bills depends on msf social worker n its team giving no tissue job n licence since my amputation five toes n needs lots of rest at home. But its ok.
Avoid the over priced mixed veg rice stall
There was also a corner for bird nerds here. The true face of Singapore cannot be imagined from Orchard or Raffles Place.
